This directory contains MMSP code applying the Method of Manufactured Solutions to the Heat Equation.
The model and notation used here comes from the first paper below, with additional contextual advice
from the second.

Send questions or comments to trevor.keller@gmail.com (Trevor Keller)

References:

1. N Malaya, KC Estacio-Hiroms, RH Stogner, KW Schulz, PT Bauman, GF Carey. "MASA: A library for verification using manufactured and analytical solutions."
   Engineering with Computers 29:487-496 (2013).
2. K Salari, P Knupp. "Code verification by the method of manufactured solutions."
   Sandia National Laboratories SAND2000-1444 (2000).
